PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of JULIE MARGARET MILLS of Ottawa, Ontario, a member of the Great Lakes Pilotage Authority, to be part-time Vice-Chairperson of the Great Lakes Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term ending on June 13, 2022.
